<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA47">
<l>tiṟattāṉ maṭaneñcē ceṉṟaṭaiva tallāl</l>
<l>peṟattāṉu mātiyō pētāy - niṟatta</l>
<l>viruvaṭikkaṇ ṇēḻaik korupāka mīntāṉ</l>
<l>ṭīruvaṭikkaṭ cērun tiru</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for going [and] nearing [him] by firmness, ignorant heart,</l>
<l>will you yourself be able to attain [it], fool – the lustre that joins the eye</l>
<l>of the sacred feet of him who gave one part to the simple woman</l>
<l>with eyes of two green mangoes by colour?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
